nodes.text: Tae Nunb was a Sullustan male. He accompanied smuggler and Cloud City Baron Administrator Lando Calrissian to the Anoat sector during the Galactic Empire's Iron Blockade of the sector following the Battle of Endor. Nunb and Calrissian operated from the Longstar Marketplace on the planet Burnin Konn, where Nunb acted as a rare goods merchant.
